Module 6: Sending Layer

This decides how to send.

If source = Freelancer:
    Send through API if allowed, otherwise manager sends manually.

If source = Remote job board:
    If email exists, send email after approval.
    If apply link exists, save manual apply task.

If source = Upwork:
    Generate proposal, manager sends inside Upwork manually/approved API.

If source = Fiverr:
    Generate reply, manager sends inside Fiverr.

If source = LinkedIn:
    Generate message, manager sends manually.

If source = Indeed:
    Generate cover letter, manager applies manually or approved flow.

Important system rule:

AI can prepare.
AI can suggest.
AI can draft.
